prompt: A stunning portrait of a young Asian woman with a gentle smile, standing indoors against a backdrop of traditional dark wood paneling. She has long, wavy dark hair adorned with an orange flower tucked behind her left ear. She is wearing a sleeveless, light teal halter-neck dress with a subtle textured floral pattern and a hint of yellow lining. She holds an antique ceramic vase with both hands at waist level, filled with a vibrant arrangement of orange autumn maple leaves and clusters of orange berries. On her wrist is a delicate pink beaded bracelet. To her left is a light woven bamboo folding screen, and to her right, a soft pink curtain drapes elegantly. The lighting is soft and diffused, highlighting her features and the textures of the scene, creating a serene and culturally rich atmosphere.
